Package: longworkR
Title: Longitudinal Employment Analytics for vecshift Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analytics and visualization tools for longitudinal employment data
    processed by the vecshift package. Includes survival analysis, impact evaluation,
    difference-in-differences, network analysis, and advanced visualization capabilities
    for employment transitions and career trajectories.
